  "html": "<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid\">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-cell \" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"cell\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-1 dnd-section kb-article-row-0-padding\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-cell dnd-column\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"cell\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-2 dnd-row\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"custom_widget\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n<div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-2\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"module\">\n\n</div>\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-3 dnd-row\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"custom_widget\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n<div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-3\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"module\">\n  <h1 id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-3_\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_inline_text_field\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"inline_text_field\">Dashboard (video)</h1>\n</div>\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-4 dnd-row\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"custom_widget\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n<div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-4\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"module\">\n  <h2 id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-4_\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_inline_text_field\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"inline_text_field\">The following is a short introduction to Data &amp; More compliance dashboard</h2>\n</div>\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-5 dnd-row\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"custom_widget\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n<div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-5\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"module\">\n  <div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-5_\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_inline_richtext_field\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"inline_richtext_field\"><p>The Dashboard has different compliance report graphs and it is possible to created new custom dashboard based on different types of parameters: eg. AD groups, Clean-up reports, sources etc.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>In the following video there is an introduction to the Compliance report dashboard:&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img class=\"hs-image-align-none\" height=\"172\" style=\"width: 68px; height: auto;\" src=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Jan-25-2023-06-37-01-3520-PM.png?width=68&amp;height=172&amp;name=image-png-Jan-25-2023-06-37-01-3520-PM.png\" width=\"68\" srcset=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Jan-25-2023-06-37-01-3520-PM.png?width=34&amp;height=86&amp;name=image-png-Jan-25-2023-06-37-01-3520-PM.png 34w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Jan-25-2023-06-37-01-3520-PM.png?width=68&amp;height=172&amp;name=image-png-Jan-25-2023-06-37-01-3520-PM.png 68w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Jan-25-2023-06-37-01-3520-PM.png?width=102&amp;height=258&amp;name=image-png-Jan-25-2023-06-37-01-3520-PM.png 102w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Jan-25-2023-06-37-01-3520-PM.png?width=136&amp;height=344&amp;name=image-png-Jan-25-2023-06-37-01-3520-PM.png 136w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Jan-25-2023-06-37-01-3520-PM.png?width=170&amp;height=430&amp;name=image-png-Jan-25-2023-06-37-01-3520-PM.png 170w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Jan-25-2023-06-37-01-3520-PM.png?width=204&amp;height=516&amp;name=image-png-Jan-25-2023-06-37-01-3520-PM.png 204w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 68px) 100vw, 68px\"></p>\n<div class=\"hs-embed-wrapper\" data-service=\"share.synthesia\"><div class=\"hs-embed-content-wrapper\"><div style=\"position: relative; overflow: hidden; aspect-ratio: 1920/1080\"><iframe src=\"https://share.synthesia.io/embeds/videos/c2493525-7678-47b9-b84d-4bbfd584f713\" loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Synthesia video player - PrivacyMonitor |&nbsp;Dashboard\" allowfullscreen=\"\" allow=\"encrypted-media; fullscreen;\" style=\"position: absolute; width: 100%; height: 100%; top: 0; left: 0; border: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; overflow:hidden;\"></iframe></div></div></div></div>\n</div>\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div>\n</div>",
